<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Damtak In Aw Mangpha</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Guol deih samgi bang khenna di'n,
 Phat leh ni a nai tai;
 Kipak nunnuom alen lai ni,
 Malai suok ding ei tai.

[V2]
 2. Na chieh na'ng tuong lam sau mahleh,
 Lalpa'n hun veng ina;
 Na vang khawpi na tun tieng leh,
 Ei hun hezing in Aw.

[V3]
 3. Lung guola ni chenga lenna,
 Buolna sau lun sungah;
 Na sakmin gen hai thei puong kau,
 Hun sawt tak nung inle.

[V4]
 4. Damtak in Aw, mangpha, mangpha,
 I kituok kit masieh;
 Chung Pathien in hun veng ina,
 Damtak in Aw, mangpha.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>287</hymn_number>
</song>